entry.title: New release for InfluxDB:
entry.content:
In addition to the list of changes below, please also see the [official release notes] (https://docs.influxdata.com/influxdb/v2.7/reference/release-notes/influxdb/) for other important information about this release.

v2.7.5 [2024/01/05]

Bug Fixes

  1. cb1701f: Only execute "init_config" on install
  2. 66ebe36: Enable Secure when using TLS and enable HttpOnly
  3. c169e98: Corrrectly return 4XX errors instead of 5XX errors
  4. 09a9607: Prevent retention service creating orphaned shard files

Features

  1. 6159c85: Add authenticating ID and user ID to request logging
  2. 6f7dc94: Write detailed logs from EDR failures

Other

  1. 306215d: Chore: emit build commands during tests
  2. 3688c45: Chore: upgrade flux

entry.title: New release for InfluxDB: 2.7.6
entry.content:
v2.7.6 [2024/04/12]

Bug Fixes

  1. bfb09aa: Panic index out of range for invalid series keys [Port to 2.7]
  2. 2a06260: Update broken flux and perf tests (2.7)
  3. e4fba98: Do not panic when empty tags are queried
  4. d2af577: Improved shard deletion
  5. 8f09e36: Return and respect cursor errors
  6. 8bc5cee: Additional constant time code

Features

  1. 6c41e97: Add optional stricter password requirements

Other

  1. 571b552: Chore: upgrade to go 1.21.6 (2.7)
  2. b2d348c: Chore: upgrade to go 1.21.8 (2.7)
  3. 3c58c06: Chore: upgrade go toolchain to 1.21.9

entry.title: New release for InfluxDB: 2.7.7
entry.content:
In addition to the list of changes below, please also see the [official release notes] (https://docs.influxdata.com/influxdb/v2.7/reference/release-notes/influxdb/) for other important information about this release.

v2.7.7 [2024/07/01]

Bug Fixes

  1. 6ac3343: Ensure TSMBatchKeyIterator and FileStore close all TSMReaders
  2. bc42088: Update logrus to 1.9.3
  3. 00b6888: Return MergeIterator.Close errors
  4. 3e756c6: GROUP BY queries with offset that crosses a DST boundary fail.
  5. 0b7cd24: Preserve time zone information in Task Scheduler
  6. e9e0f74: Prevent retention service from hanging

Features

  1. 852a03d: Disable file:// urls when hardening enabled

Other

  1. 46d9540: Chore: update golang.org/x/net to v0.23.0 (2.7)
  2. 9cec3d0: Chore: upgrade protocol buffers to v5.26.1
  3. c6c00b8: Build(flux): update flux to v0.195.1
  4. 26db97e: Chore: upgrade go toolchain to 1.21.10
